      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+2\n\nThere are also probably many other places in the code that use a semaphore when they should instead be using a mutex. Some of the Lustre code predates the time when there was a separate mutex type and has never been moved over.\n\nCould you please make one or more separate patches to convert semaphore users over to mutex if possible.",
